        function toggleCheckBoxes(obj) {
            var theForm = document.getElementById("thePage:SiteTemplate:theForm");
            for (var i=0; i<theForm.elements.length; i++){
                if (theForm.elements[i].type=="checkbox" && theForm.elements[i].name != obj.name) {
                    theForm.elements[i].checked = false;
                }
            }
        }
        
        // ATLAS-1089: back & continue buttons showing twice for Reserved Group/Emergency Appointments
        function checkIfButtonsShowTwice() {
            
            // from 1st form
            var continueBtn = document.getElementById("thePage:SiteTemplate:theForm:continueBtn");
            var backBtn = document.getElementById("thePage:SiteTemplate:theForm:backBtn");
            
            // from 2nd form
            var continueBtnToHide = document.getElementById("thePage:SiteTemplate:theForm2:continueBtn");
            var backBtnToHide = document.getElementById("thePage:SiteTemplate:theForm2:form2BackBtn");
                        
            // the controller logic for rendering the buttons is fragile so... front end solutions ftw
            if(continueBtn != null){
              if (continueBtnToHide != null) {  
                  continueBtnToHide.style.display = "none";
              }
            }
            
            if(backBtn != null){
              if (backBtnToHide != null) {
                  backBtnToHide.style.display = "none";
              }
            }
        }
         
         // ATLAS-1036
         var btnBg;            
         function checkIfTimeWasSelected()
         {
            var theForm = document.getElementById("thePage:SiteTemplate:theForm");
            //var theForm2 = document.getElementById("thePage:SiteTemplate:theForm");
            var timeSelected = false;
            
            // see if applicant has selected a time
            for (var i=0; i<theForm.elements.length; i++){
                if (theForm.elements[i].type=="checkbox" && theForm.elements[i].checked === true) {
                    timeSelected = true;
                    break;
                }               
            }               
             
            //alert(dateSelected);
            
            // 2 buttons to disable --> schedule appointment button and continue button (on ofc form)
            var btn = document.getElementById("thePage:SiteTemplate:theForm:addItem");
            var continueBtn = document.getElementById("thePage:SiteTemplate:theForm:continueBtn");
            
            //alert(btn);
            //alert(continueBtn);
            
            if (timeSelected) {
                if (btn != null) {
                    btn.disabled = false;
                    btn.style.background = btnBg;
                    btn.style.color = 'white'; 
                }             
                
                if (continueBtn != null) {
                    continueBtn.disabled = false;
                    continueBtn.style.background = btnBg;
                    continueBtn.style.color = 'white';
                }
            } else {
                if (btn != null) {
                    btn.disabled = true;
                    btn.style.background = 'gray';
                    btn.style.color = 'black';
                }
                
                if (continueBtn != null) {
                    continueBtn.disabled = true;
                    continueBtn.style.background = 'gray';
                    continueBtn.style.color = 'black';
                }
            }
         
          }
       
        var myDayHash = new Array();
            myDayHash['27-10-2021'] = true;
            myDayHash['28-10-2021'] = true;
        var ofcAptDateStr = null;ofcAptDateStr = ''; 
        
        var splitDate = 'Wed Oct 27 00:00:00 GMT 2021'.split(" ");
        var minApptDate = splitDate[1] + ' ' + splitDate[2] + ' ' + splitDate[5];
        
        $().ready(function() {
            $("#datepicker").datepicker({   
                monthNames: ['January','February','March','April','May','June','July','August','September','October','November','December'],              
                numberOfMonths: 3,
                minDate: new Date(minApptDate),                 
                defaultDate: new Date(minApptDate),
                beforeShowDay: function(date) {
                    var dateString = date.getDate()+"-"+(date.getMonth()+1)+"-"+date.getFullYear();
                    if (ofcAptDateStr != null){
                        ofcAptDate = new Date(ofcAptDateStr);
                        if (ofcAptDate.toString() == date.toString()) {
                            return [myDayHash[dateString], "highlighted", "OFC Appointment Date"];
                        } else if (myDayHash[dateString]){
                            return [true,""];
                        } else {
                            return [false,"ui-state-active","Unavailable"];
                        }
                    } else {
                        if (myDayHash[dateString]){
                            return [true, ""];
                        }
                        else {
                            return [false,"ui-state-active","Unavailable"];
                        }
                    }
                      
                },
                onSelect: function(dateText, inst) { 
                    getScheduleEntries(dateText);
                }
            });

            $( "input.button" ).button();
            
            // ATLAS-1036
            // get original bg color of button
            var tempBtn = document.getElementById("thePage:SiteTemplate:theForm:addItem");
            if (tempBtn != null) {
                btnBg = tempBtn.style.background;
            } else {
                btnBg = document.getElementById("thePage:SiteTemplate:theForm:continueBtn").style.background;
            }
            
            
            // start off disabled
            checkIfTimeWasSelected();
            checkIfButtonsShowTwice(); // ATLAS-1089
        });
